# Standalone-exe build artifacts — built on demand, never committed (see PACKAGING.md).
# Only the spec (mira-plc-parser.spec) and PACKAGING.md are tracked; the per-platform
# binary and PyInstaller's working dir are not.
/build/
/dist/

# CLI report outputs written during local runs / tests (<stem>.report.md/.json, <stem>.i3x.json).
*.report.md
*.report.json
*.i3x.json
# ...EXCEPT the golden snapshots, which are the committed report@1 / i3x@1 contracts (not run output).
!tests/fixtures/golden/*.report.json
!tests/fixtures/golden/*.i3x.json
